Class MappedMappingRegistry<K,V,M extends Map<K,V>>

java.lang.Object
cn.nukkit.registry.mappings.MappingRegistry<M>
cn.nukkit.registry.mappings.AbstractMappedRegistry<K,V,M>
cn.nukkit.registry.mappings.MappedMappingRegistry<K,V,M>
Type Parameters:
K - the key
V - the value
M - the map
public class MappedMappingRegistry<K,V,M extends Map<K,V>> extends AbstractMappedRegistry<K,V,M>
An public registry holding a map of various registrations as defined by MappedMappingRegistry. The M represents the map class, which can be anything that extends Map. The MappedMappingRegistry and MappedMappingRegistry generics are the key and value respectively.
